title: Compaq Presario 7100 series QuickRestore CD & Floppy
description:
This is the original restore CD and floppy disk for the mid-90s Compaq Presario 7100 series of PCs. Finding drivers etc for old PCs can be frustrating so I thought I'd share this in case it was of any use to somebody.

The CD contains the full MS-DOS 6.2 & Windows 3.1 installation along with various other programs that came pre-installed. It includes UK English, German, and Dutch languages - I think it is automatically selected depending on which model system you have.

The restore program will only run on supported PCs unfortunately.

Enjoy
